4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for beginners interested in pursuing a career in cybersecurity. The program lasts 16 weeks and includes three live online classes per week, with class sizes capped at 16 participants. Students will acquire foundational skills in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration. Key topics include cloud security, penetration testing, and cyber threat intelligence. Participants will also learn about risk management and international compliance standards. Upon completion, candidates receive an official certificate recognized by various institutions. The bootcamp is available in English and Spanish. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop